Student Performance Advisor - Knowledge Based System
1.Problem Being Solved

Many students struggle to evaluate their academic performance and identify factors affecting their success.This Knowledge-Based System acts as a Student Performance Advisor by analyzing student related information such as attendance, assignment completion, study habits, motivation, participation, project completion and exam performance.
The system applies rule-based reasoning to provide conclusions and recommendations that can help students improve their academic outcomes.

